                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-937-18520920 t18520920-937-punishment-65"></join>Confined Twelve Months</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>(<hi rend="italic">There was another indictment against the prisoner, for obtaining goods by similar pretences.</hi>)</p>
